org.springframework.data.redis.core.script

接口 RedisScript<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The script result type. Should be one of Long, Boolean, List, or deserialized value type. Can be if the script returns a throw-away status (i.e "OK")
    所有已知实现类:
    DefaultRedisScript

    public interface RedisScript<T>
    A script to be executed using the Redis scripting support available as of version 2.6

      • getSha1

        String getSha1()
        返回:
        The SHA1 of the script, used for executing Redis evalsha command.

      • getResultType

        @Nullable
Class<T> getResultType()
        返回:
        The script result type. Should be one of Long, Boolean, List, or deserialized value type. null if the script returns a throw-away status (i.e "OK").

      • getScriptAsString

        返回:
